name: Stella Somnia
body:
## Control

*   [Avatar controls 1](https://cdn.rawgit.com/skymaiden/stella-somnia-prototypes/master/proto_controls1/index.html): tap left half to move left, tap right half to move right, swipe any direction to jump.
*   [Avatar controls 2](https://cdn.rawgit.com/skymaiden/stella-somnia-prototypes/master/proto_controls2/index.html): tap avatar left to move left, tap avatar right to move right, swipe any direction to jump.
